\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;line-height:200%;\">、研讨内容：<span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;line-height:200%;\">（<span><span>1</span>）培养方案的形成过程（包括各专业外出调研、校内研讨和校外专家论证等情况）。（时间控制在<span>5</span>分钟）<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;line-height:200%;\">（<span><span>2</span>）培养目标定位、理论课程体系优化、实践教学体系构建、学时学分总量及分布、体现的培养特色等相关内容。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;line-height:200%;\">（<span><span>3</span>）与<span>2012</span>版相比，课程体系和实践体系的调整情况。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;line-height:200%;\">（<span><span>4</span>）其他教学相关问题。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;line-height:200%;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;line-height:200%;\">、研讨形式：<span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;line-height:200%;\">各系、部主任以<span><span>ppt</span>形式进行汇报，参会人员适时补充。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;line-height:200%;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;line-height:200%;\">、参会人员：<span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;line-height:200%;\">各系部主任、副主任、教研室主任、实验室主任和相关教师。<span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;line-height:200%;\">各系、部提供<span><span>2014</span>版培养方案纸质文档一式<span>7</span>份，以备研讨交流。具体时间安排另行通知。<span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;line-height:200%;\">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24pt;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;line-height:200%;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;line-height:200%;\">教务处</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;line-height:200%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;line-height:200%;\">二〇一四年三月二十日</span>','2014-04-19 18:29:23','2014-04-19 18:29:23'),(17,'关于开展校外实习基地重点建设专项活动的通知','<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">校外实习基地是大学生进行实践训练的主要载体</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">是培养应用型人才的重要途径</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">。</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-size:12pt;\"><span>2015</span></span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">年我院将迎来教育部合格评估，校外实习基地建设是评估的一项重要指标。我院校外实习基地建设</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">虽然</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">在近几年得到了较大的发展，取得了明显的成绩，但距培养高素质应用型人才的培养目标还存在着一定的差距</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">主要表现在：校外实习基地数量还不能完全满足毕业生的实习需求；校外实习基地建设缺乏广泛性，实效性；校外实习基地管理方式简单松弛，不能有效地评估考核</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">；</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">校外基地远离学校，学校与实习基地缺乏深度联系</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">、</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">缺乏长期互惠互利的合作模式等。基于这种现状，</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">我院本年度将开展实习基地重点建设专项活动，</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">尽快在省内建设一批具有示范性</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">、</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">实践效果好和长期稳定的实习基地，并充分挖掘其潜在的资源，使之成为培养应用型人才的摇篮</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">。<span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24.6pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">活动目的：</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24.6pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">培养学生的专业技能和职业素质</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">促进学生就业</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">；</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">提升学生的综合素质</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">培养学生的创新精神、实践能力及适应社会的能力。</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:18pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">活动内容：<span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\" class=\"MsoBodyText\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">1.</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">对省内周边企事业、研究所等单位进行充分调研、论证，结合</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">本系部<span style=\"color:black;\"><span>实际，探索校企多种融合方式和专业特色的人才培养新途径。<span></span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\" class=\"MsoBodyText\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">2.</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">系部通过组织调研和讨论，形成思路清晰，教学任务明确，切实可行的校外实习基地建设方案。<span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:28pt;background:white;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">3. </span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">根据专业特点积极与周边相关企事业、科研院所等单位进行沟通、联系，争取与行业领域内具有鲜明的特色和明显的优势、具备丰富经验和良好条件、能够承担大学生实践教学任务的单位建立长期稳定的合作关系。每专业至少建设一个签署正式合作协议并挂牌的校外实习基地。<span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:28pt;background:white;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">4. </span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">在学生实习或挂牌过程中，学院将组织专门人员实地考察实习条件及效果。<span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">校外实习基地建设为</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;color:black;font-size:12pt;\"><span>2014</span></span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">年度重点建设专项活动，</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;color:black;font-size:12pt;\"><span>12</span></span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">月</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;color:black;font-size:12pt;\"><span>31</span></span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">日前</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">各系部根据校外实习基地建设落实情况写出专项工作总结，并将总结报告提交教务处实践教学科（纸质文档一式一份），电子文档发到</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;color:black;font-size:12pt;\"><a href=\"mailto:%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E5%8F%91%E5%88%B0tgjyk3566044@126.com\"><span style=\"color:black;text-decoration:none;\"><span>tgsjk3566064@126.com</span></span></a></span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">。</span><span style=\"line-height:200%;color:black;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">教务处</span></span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-size:12pt;\"><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">二〇一四年三月十三日</span></span>','2014-04-19 18:29:51','2014-04-19 18:29:51');
